        <section id="id12613603">
          <title>DIE MERKWAARDIGE MILJOEN!</title>
          <para id="id19537782">Jy weet reeds:</para>
          <para id="id27175003">10 x 10 = 100</para>
          <para id="id27347288">100 x 10 = 1 000</para>
          <para id="id17721033">1 000 x 10 = 10 000</para>
          <para id="id16988478">10 000 x 10 = 100 000</para>
          <para id="id12655246">Kyk goed na die patroon hierbo en vul in:</para>
          <para id="id16222066">100 000 x 10 = ______________________________________________________</para>
          <para id="id4559844"><emphasis effect="bold">Korrek!</emphasis> 100 000 x 10 = 1 000 000</para>
          <para id="id7556531">Ons lees: 1 000 000 eenmiljoen</para>
          <list id="id5585425" list-type="bulleted">
            <item>In the notation column it looks like this:</item>
          </list>
